# Tools

* Shell: zsh (OMZ)
* ZSH plugins: 
  * zsh-autosuggestions
  * zsh-syntax-highlighting
* Terminal: alacritty
* Prompt: starship
* VCS: git
* Editors: nvim + helix
* Multiplexer: zellij (cargo)
* Better ls: eza (cargo)
* Better cat: batcat
* Gnome extensions - run-or-raise

# Configuration files

.zshrc     -> ~/.zshrc
.zfunc     -> ~/.zfunc
.gitconfig -> ~/.gitconfig
.config/nvim          -> ~/.config/nvim
.config/alacritty     -> ~/.config/alacritty
.config/zellij        -> ~/.config/zellij
.config/starship.toml -> ~/.config/starship.toml
.config/helix         -> ~/.config/helix
.config/run-or-raise  -> ~/.config/run-or-raise

# Font
* MesloLGS NF: fonts/

